  "id": "cli/add",
  "title": "ng add",
  "contents": "\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/add\", \"name\": \"add\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-add\">ng add<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/add#ng-add\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>为你的项目添加对外部库的支持。</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">add</span> &#x3C;<var>collection</var>>\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------mode_edit--code--------说明----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/add/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.0.3/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/add/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        说明\n    </h2>\n    <p>将已发布库的 npm 包添加到你的工作区，并按照库中原理图的指示把当前工作目录中的项目配置为使用该库。例如，添加<code>@angular/pwa</code> 会把你的项目配置为支持 PWA 的：</p>\n<code-example language=\"bash\">\n ng add @angular/pwa\n</code-example>\n\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">参数</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th width=\"15%\">参数</th>\n      <th width=\"40%\">说明</th>\n      <th>值类型</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">collection</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>要添加的包。</p>\n\n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">选项</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th width=\"15%\">选项</th>\n    <th width=\"40%\">说明</th>\n    <th>值类型</th>\n    <th>默认值</th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--defaults</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>对有默认值的选项禁用交互式输入提示。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--dry-run</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>运行一遍并汇报其活动轨迹，但不真的写入任何结果。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--force</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>强制覆盖现存文件。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在控制台显示关于本命令的帮助信息。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--interactive</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>启用交互式输入提示。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--registry</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>要使用的 NPM registry。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">string</code></td>\n    <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--skip-confirmation</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在安装和执行包之前跳过询问确认提示。在使用此选项之前，请确保包名称是正确的。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td>\n      <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--verbose</code>\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      \n      <p>在执行期间显示内部操作的详细信息。</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n    <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/npm-packages\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/add#ng-add\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/add/long-description.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.0.3/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/add/long-description.md\n-->"
